{{Infobox country at games | NOC = UZB | NOCname = [[National Olympic Committee of the Republic of Uzbekistan]] | oldcode = | year = 2006 | date = | games = Asian Games | location = [[Doha]] | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | officials = | gold = 11 | silver = 14 | bronze = 15 | rank = 7 | appearances = auto | seealso = | website = }}
'''[[Uzbekistan]]''' competed in the '''[[2006 Asian Games|15th Asian Games]]''', officially known as the '''XV Asiad''' held in [[Doha]], [[Qatar]] from December 1 to December 15, 2006. Uzbekistan ranked 7th with 11 gold medals in this edition of the [[Asian Games|Asiad]].<ref>[http://www.ocasia.org/Game/MWinner.aspx?AMWCode=19&GCode=1 Overall Medal Standings - Doha 2006]</ref>
